EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   01 THRU 06 AUG WITHIN 34 MILES OF:
   A. 57-43.0N 009-12.8W.
   B. 57-08.0N 008-47.7W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16
   OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1601/16(35),
   OPERATIONS COMPLETED.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 062000Z AUG 16.
